<lb ed="C I" n="0203a01"/>　　度蓋行佛主陳<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">熬</unclear>樂　水月光佛主陳歸歡　　　　日光佛主清信邵賜好　　最上首佛主清信王那姿　　日月流<note n="0203001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18853;＝璃【史語所】</note><app n="0203001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18853;</rdg></app>光佛主陳洪暢妻杜容姬　　　功德多寶佛主陳洪建
<lb ed="C I" n="0203a02"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0203a03"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0203a04"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0203a05"/>淨信佛主　　　　　　　除疑<note n="0203002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30995;＝冥【史語所】</note><app n="0203002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30995;</rdg></app>佛主陳黑　　　　　花色王佛主清信張舍妃　菩提華佛主清信荊元妃　　旡上流<app source="0203001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18853;</rdg></app>光佛主陳洪興　　　　　　　<note n="0203003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06924;＝開【史語所】</note><app n="0203003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">開</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06924;</rdg></app>日月光佛主陳洪度
<lb ed="C I" n="0203a06"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0203a07"/>
